  "title": "Run-Length Encoding",
  "description": "Write a function `solve(input)` that takes a string and returns its run-length encoding. Each run of consecutive identical characters should be replaced with the character followed by the count.",
  "examples": [
    { "input": "aaabbc", "output": "a3b2c1" },
    { "input": "wwwwaaadexxxxxx", "output": "w4a3d1e1x6" }
